Class JavaSparkExecutionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.cdap.api.spark.JavaSparkExecutionContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RuntimeContext, SecureStore, Transactional, WorkflowInfoProvider

    @Beta
public abstract class JavaSparkExecutionContext
extends Object
implements RuntimeContext, Transactional, WorkflowInfoProvider, SecureStore
    Spark program execution context. User Spark program can interact with CDAP through this context.

        datasetName - name of the Dataset
        arguments - arguments for the Dataset
        Throws:
        DatasetInstantiationException - if the Dataset doesn't exist
